item.title: 264: PATREON UNLOCKED (Two Minis XI)
item.description: While Brian's away, the gamers will play! And by "play," we mean rerunning some minisodes from our Patreon on the main feed. We do these every week for folks on our $5 tier, and if you enjoy solo eps where it's just Brian and Leighton, that's basically what these are in bite-sized form. The two minis we have here are Blorp! from January 15th and Respection of Rejection from March 12th... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/670ed8c695a9a2047556318e
